_sText:
This is a base version of the map for all the other versions I'll make, such as cs, zm, maybe gg, and maybe for hl2 dm. And added buyzones now.
I found some bugs, due to microbrushes, but they won't be on the final version.
The water appears black some times, I didn't figured out what is causing that, but it has something to do with hdr and bloom, so play a little bit with the graphics settings and the water will eventually appear correctly. If you happen to figure out why the water appears bloack let me know.
KEEP UP THE FEEDBACK GUYS!
